WEBVTT

00:01.189 --> 00:07.510
In 2013, he was part of the team that built the mega container vessel, the Triple E.

00:11.029 --> 00:13.881
Now, Peter's wrangling his own team...

00:14.859 --> 00:17.695
...as it gears up for one of its toughest builds to date:...

00:20.789 --> 00:23.573
...the 10,000-ton Maersk Tangier,...

00:24.102 --> 00:27.551
...designed to carry everything from petroleum to palm oil.

00:29.559 --> 00:34.039
She's one of a fleet of ten tankers being built over the next two years.

00:39.671 --> 00:45.329
Peter and the team have just 23 weeks to assemble and launch their new tanker.

00:51.469 --> 00:55.337
If the shipyard misses the deadline, there will be some penalties for the shipyard.

00:56.102 --> 01:00.560
And of course, we will have a not happy owner because they can't get the ship.

